{"tid":109640,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"點解以前大家打PM咁鬼柒","createTime":"2017-02-06T06:00:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-07T14:36:31.000Z","uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"80de56282d055de8093b8ce1ffffdc4556ba7838","tid":109640,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T06:00:37.000Z","msg":"剛剛先check post見到D人打小剛又無力，打小茜又被人逆推。根本其實只要用其他寵就屈到佢，小剛那個去石英高原閘口下方草叢就有隻猴怪比你爆碎石頭。仲有大家都係驚小茜招放電眼，只要捉隻雌性就已經廢左大奶5成武功，之後黃金市下方腕力，撞樹克拉，同捉蟲大會大甲三選一爆瓦片過肩摔就打到大奶出曬閪水。迷宮仲白癡，真心唔明推幾嚿石頭都可以卡成2，三個鐘，真係唔得咪上奇異種子維基，gamefaq一招擊殺。好心班人打道館前check下附近有咩寵捉啦！打pm同做數學題一樣，最緊要睇餸食飯架。最後馬志士迷題試幾次咪得囉，第二個機關必定在第一個機關的四個方向，25%人品差都唔會打到要棄坑吧？btw旁邊的地鼠洞穴係用來打佢隻雷超唔係突然毫無原因出現，明白未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下次都係開台打金心版去，上次開台4個半鐘打爆黃版，洗鬼打成個星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自己打黑暗魔王黃版睇返，都已經成年前..."},{"pid":"95050239a01644273d7103b9d2e97e78f3bcb60f","tid":109640,"uid":20611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T06:03:19.000Z","msg":"腕力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大甲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c06dff1371f2b05b01c943a9ec74730a4924f20d","tid":109640,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T06:31:33.000Z","msg":"嘩 好叻呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下下睇攻略既廢人唔會明自己摸索隻game既樂趣"},{"pid":"c40cfd9682fc40c0aaa3a7b68c861a525020eb8b","tid":109640,"uid":34503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T06:37:38.000Z","msg